{
  "name": "focustube-frontend",
  "version": "1.1.0",
  "author": "Kamrul Hasan",
  "description": "FocusTube (Frontend) is the client-side repository for the FocusTube web app — a distraction-free learning platform built on top of YouTube. It provides a clean and intuitive interface for users to access YouTube content without distractions, allowing them to focus on their learning. The frontend is built using Next.js, React, and Tailwind CSS, ensuring a responsive and seamless user experience across devices.",
